node.text:
Santa Monica Studios teased us with Thor during the God Of War Ragnarok trailer, but soon after, art director Raf Grassetti shared a full image of the God Of Thunder... 👇

It's safe to say he might not be what a lot of fans were expecting, but we absolutely love him. This Thor isn't exactly the ripped muscular poster boy that fans of Marvel comic books and movies might be used to, but that's not what he's supposed to look like!

TL;DR: This version of Thor is awesome. He looks powerful, imposing, and completely terrifying. We can't wait to see him go a few rounds with Kratos next year.
